parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning automatic high-beam system can cause accidents, road rage, and distractions, as it fails to dim or switches between high and low beams erratically, blinding oncoming drivers.
symptoms: The high beams stay on with oncoming traffic
turn off when seeing a road sign
flash on and off repeatedly
fail to dim in a timely fashion
or do not engage high beams when needed. The system is overly sensitive to reflections from road signs and mile markers
causing it to switch between high and low beams.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission system can cause the vehicle to lose power, making it difficult or impossible to accelerate, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle goes into limp mode
the Check Engine Light (CEL) flashes
the engine runs rough and idles hard
the vehicle loses power and acceleration
the vehicle shuts down cylinders
the vehicle is unable to exceed 30 mph.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unexpected shift of the transmission into neutral can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, making it difficult or impossible to accelerate, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shifts into neutral while driving
the vehicle shifts into neutral when exiting a freeway
the transmission alert comes on
the vehicle loses power and acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Safety Concerns with Manual Transmission Neutral
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The design flaw of the manual transmission neutral system can cause the vehicle to roll or become stuck in a hazardous location, making it difficult or impossible to safely move the vehicle.
symptoms: The vehicle cannot be safely moved when stuck in a hazardous location
the manual transmission neutral system requires a special tool that is not readily available
the location of the bolt to manually lock the transmission in neutral is hazardous.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the backup camera can cause reduced visibility while reversing, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The backup camera screen goes black
displays a blank screen
or fails to function intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Loss of Power and Engine Stalling
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The loss of power and engine stalling can cause accidents, especially when merging into heavy traffic or navigating intersections.
symptoms: The check engine light comes on
the vehicle loses power
and the engine shutters or stalls
making it difficult to accelerate or maintain speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the auto start/stop function can cause the vehicle to stall in traffic, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The auto start/stop function fails to restart the engine after stopping
leaving the vehicle stranded in traffic or intersections.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water leaks can cause corrosion of wires and electrical components, leading to electrical failures, fires, or other safety hazards.
symptoms: Water is leaking into the bed of the truck
apparently through the carpet below the backseat area
which could lead to corrosion of wires and electrical components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rodent damage to the wiring harness can cause electrical failures, fires, or other safety hazards.
symptoms: Warning lights flash
and the vehicle goes into limp mode
rendering it unable to drive
due to rodent damage to the wiring harness.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Wireless Charger Failure and Fire Hazard
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wireless charger can cause overheating, potentially leading to fires or explosions.
symptoms: The wireless charger fails to charge phones
makes them hot
and disconnects and reconnects repeatedly
posing a fire hazard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The audio system volume adjustment issue can cause distraction while driving, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The audio system adjusts volume erratically when connected to Android Auto or Bluetooth
causing a strange sound or volume fluctuation.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden explosion of the moonroof glass can cause a startling and potentially dangerous situation for the driver and passengers, with flying glass fragments posing a risk of injury.
symptoms: Moonroof glass explodes outward without being struck by debris
showering the interior with glass fragments.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear view camera can increase the risk of accidents or injuries when reversing, particularly in situations where visibility is limited.
symptoms: The rear view camera displays a black screen
failing to provide a clear view of the area behind the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Auto Engine Idle Shut Off Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning auto engine idle shut off feature can cause unexpected shifts into park, potentially leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The engine shuts off when the vehicle comes to a stop
and the truck shifts into park when the engine restarts
occurring about 75% of the time.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning automatic high beam assist can cause distractions or disruptions to oncoming traffic, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The high beams turn on and off constantly
picking up reflections on dark roads
staying on when other cars are approaching
and flashing on and off at cars approaching.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The poorly designed infotainment system can distract the driver, requiring excessive interaction to function properly, and potentially increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The system displays warnings and requires multiple button presses to function
even when not connected to a device
and has too many settings that require excessive interaction.
